<s> Total turnover in Glaxo was a thin 975,000 shares . </s>
<s> In Tokyo , stocks had a second-consecutive loss Monday in quiet trading with the exception of concentrated buying in some incentive-backed issues . </s>
<s> The Nikkei index of 225 selected issues fell 109.85 points to 35417.44 . </s>
<s> The index fell 151.20 Friday . </s>
<s> In early trading in Tokyo Tuesday , the Nikkei index rose 35.28 points to 35452.72 . </s>
